name: Alti-electronics
overview: Alti-electronics Co., Ltd. manufactures and sells hi-tech products for the electronics industry, primarily in Korea and Japan, as well as in North America. The company operates in Mobile Phone, Semiconductor, and Telecommunication Device divisions. The Mobile Phone division offers cellular phone parts, such as press terminals, die-castings, external parts, and various hinge mechanisms, as well as super-thin cast-molding products to consumer products companies. The Semiconductor division manufactures and sells light-emitting diode products for various applications in smart phones, pocket PCs, spot watches, tablet PCs, and digital cameras. The Telecommunication Device division provides switchboard parts, base station heat exchangers, base station cabinets, and various intermediate cabinets, as well as total engineering service and solution, heat analysis, design detail, parts development, cable form/wire harness, and assembly services. The company, formerly known as Ail Industry Co., was founded in 1972 and is headquartered in Seoul, the Republic of Korea.
